<L>__{interior squad car moving that moment}
<A>__{the cops in the car react in astonishment as pigeons begin hurling themselves at the windshields. a dozen kamikaze birds bounce off in rapid succession. cracks begin to spread across the glass. the cops can't see where they're driving. the car swerves wildly. and still the pigeons keep coming covering the windshield totally obscuring the streets from view...}
<L>__{exterior streets on squad cars that moment}
<A>__{the first car, completely covered with birds, smacks into a lamppost and skids. the second car crashes into it. and the pigeons continue to pour down from the heavens, swarming onto the immobilized squad cars.}
